snippet: Hosni Mubarak, the former president of Egypt, returned to court in Cairo in the killings of about 900 protesters during the 2011 uprising.
abstract: Former Egyptian Pres Hosni Mubarak appears healthy and grinning in court as trial resumes on charges related to killings of protesters during 2011 uprising that led to his ouster.
lead_paragraph: Hosni Mubarak, the former president of Egypt, returned to court in Cairo in the killings of about 900 protesters during the 2011 uprising.
